Men's Doubles Final:
</P>
<P>
Kong Linghui/Liu Guoliang, China, vs Jorg Rosskopf,
Germany/Vladimir Samsonov, Belarus
</P>
<P>
Women's Doubles Final:
</P>
<P>
Li Ju/Wang Nan, China, vs Park Hae Jung/Kim Moo Kyu, South
Korea
</P>
