exchanges, enhancing understanding, strengthening friendship and
promoting cooperation between the media, publishing,
broadcasting, film and Television circles of the two countries.
</P>
<P>
Ding expressed his hope that the news media of the two
countries should play an active role in promoting the friendship
between the people of the two countries from generation to
generation.
</P>
