<HEADLINE> Ningbo Works Hard at Export-oriented Agriculture </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
NINGBO December 21 (Xinhua) -- With favourable natural
conditions and a correct policy of the local government,
export-oriented agriculture in Ningbo has served as an important
driving force to propel the development of rural economy.
</P>
<P>
The coastal city, located in east China's Zhejiang province, is
expected to realize 300 million US dollars in the export of
agricultural products this year, 3.8 times of that in 1990.
</P>
<P>
