co-operative enterprises and wholly foreign-funded companies in
the agricultural sectors. And 14 of them involve an investment of
over 10 million US dollars each.
</P>
<P>
Meanwhile, the city has set up a group of bases for producing
and exporting vegetable, fruit, flowers, poultry and aquatic
products.
</P>
<P>
In addition, the city owns 48 ships used for deep-sea fishing,
with an annual output reaching 7,600 tons.
</P>
<P>
